{"tid":2463722,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葉劉：感謝黨讚賞 為主權發聲並非有意刷鞋 涉疆品牌不用燒 停用即可","createTime":"2021-03-27T02:43:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T03:00:30.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a3391dc9aa6896711002ab39d6c3049fb35e6270","tid":2463722,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T02:43:50.000Z","msg":"葉劉淑儀感激國台辦點名稱讚　形容是「無意的收獲」 <br />\n<br />\n行政會議成員、新民黨主席葉劉淑儀日前被國台辦發言人朱鳳蓮點名稱讚，指她在一場外媒主辦的研討會上，離場抗議有與會者指「台灣是國家」，是表達正義之聲，作出有力批駁。葉劉淑儀表示，感激國台辦的讚揚，形容是無意的收獲，說答應出席研討會前，不知道同場有「台獨份子」。 <br />\n<br />\n葉劉淑儀又表示，已決定停買及停用牽涉「新疆棉風波」的品牌產品，但不認為需要採取進一步行動，包括銷毀現有產品。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2384826\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2384826&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWqjD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=5cebf2f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2384826</a>"},{"pid":"da24b0d24cdf62aa94a5cbf8e3508dbaa675a758","tid":2463722,"uid":126226,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T02:44:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔燒都應該掉撚左佢啦...停用"},{"pid":"1e04d6929e20d063b6fd897f63fe77b9ef187d6d","tid":2463722,"uid":55533,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T02:44:42.000Z","msg":"但不認為需要採取進一步行動，包括銷毀現有產品。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n假愛国"},{"pid":"8b57d51f23e6cb544cbf8dabc9f6eb3258eea592","tid":2463722,"uid":124400,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T02:46:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fy5uyqb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFy5uyqb.gif&h=c4c39e1c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e10679a8c86a73aae78f30a81b5bae1507fc6e6e","tid":2463722,"uid":33939,"like":3,"dislike":0,"sc